name: Gather Community Plant #009 - Ben Laorg
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from HicEtNunc artists and their artistic renditions of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

Ben Laorg creates eerie pieces of glitch art, and has multiple series underway in his weird style.

Collecting this plant directly supports the GatherArt Foundation & the artist who planted this CleanNFT.
